      "date": "2011-05-24 13:00:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/40bfa394-8605-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af).  Ran 15 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
